description: [``botocore``] Update endpoint-rules client to latest version
[``botocore``] Adds support for InferredSecondaryAddress place type, Designator in SecondaryAddressComponent and Heading in ReverseGeocode.

[``botocore``] This release adds support for the Registration Reviewer feature, which provides generative AI feedback on a phone number or sender ID registration to ensure completeness before sending to downstream (carrier) review.
[``botocore``] Add additional validation to Outpost bucket names.
